, \"from\": 738, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"200m\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon runner Caireses\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"Marathonin\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"a remarkable time\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking of her ambitions at this year's games, Asher-Smith seems confident.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her ambitions\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's games\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am running great,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy that as we are coming into the crunch time in the season everything's coming together.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crunch time\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am on track.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to be so successful, I want to do myself proud and I want to create history.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not my first rodeo and I am very excited going into my third Olympic Games in a really good place.\\\"\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first rodeo\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"my third Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good place\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers may be used to seeing Olympic running tracks in a rust-red hue, but in Paris, athletes can look forward to competing on a purple track.\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.7512600715058797e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Viewers\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"a rust-red hue\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"a purple track\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alain Blondel, sports manager in charge of athletics for Paris 2024, said the decision was a creative one.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Blondel\", \"score\": 0.9999990810651654, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alain Blondel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Blondel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Blondel\"}, {\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1269243566173198e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports manager\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The big part of the job was to come up with a track that was different from what we had seen, to maintain the creative approach that the Organising Committee has had since it was set up, to go a little bit outside the box,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The big part\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"a track\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"the creative approach\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the Organising Committee\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"the box\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The look of the Games includes three colours for all the competition venues: blue, green and purple.\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The look\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"three colours\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"purple\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We decided on this purple track with different tones: lighter for the track, darker for the service areas, and grey for the turns at the end of the bend, reminding of the ash-coloured tracks that were there 100 years ago for the Olympic Games Paris 1924.\\\"\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this purple track\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"different tones\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the service areas\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"the turns\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"the bend\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"the ash-coloured tracks\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who else than Carl Lewis to unveil our purple track \\ud83d\\udc9cThe Stade de France is more than ready for the Athletics event this summer.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2208, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our purple track\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"The Stade de France\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"the Athletics event\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Be ready, this track will be faaaast \\u26a1pic.twitter.com/cmxzDaVIzH He added: \\\"We had to work hard on the colours, so that they came out in the best possible tones to highlight the athletes.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this track\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"the colours\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible tones\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a track, it has to be pretty, but above all it's a stage on which the athletes are going to perform.\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a track\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"a stage\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's really important is that the colours and the athletes stand out.\\\"\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the colours\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tony Estanguet, president of Paris 2024, said this year's Olympic aesthetic comprised elegance, creativity and the \\\"French art de vivre\\\".\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2695, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1269243566173198e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6625594028178758, \"rank\": 0.4636795126311753, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympic aesthetic comprised elegance\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The purple track intends to convey a \\\"joyful and festive tone\\\", he added.\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The purple track\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"joyful and festive tone\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was designed by Italian company Mondo, which has been responsible for every Olympic track since 1976.\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2928, \"end\": 2935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.998521587338569, \"rank\": 0.0014559002904371184, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r