ate\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"a substance\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"resilient flooring\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shells are cleaned and ground into a powder to use in the tracks.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The shells\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"a powder\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3353}, {\"ngram\": \"the tracks\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alessandro Piceli, a research and development manager at Mondo, claims that their current purple iteration is even better than that used at the 2020 Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3435, \"end\": 3440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\", \"score\": 0.9838833905616808, \"rank\": 0.01630890304513712, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alessandro Piceli\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"a research and development manager\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"their current purple iteration\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3483}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are focusing on the dynamic connection between the track and a new generation of shoes,\\\" he toldThe Guardian.\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dynamic connection\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"a new generation\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3621}, {\"ngram\": \"shoes\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For the track, we only see the aesthetics, but there is great work that goes into the underlayer.\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ng